text: Julie Beth Hagerty (born June 15, 1955) is an American actress and former model. She starred as Elaine in the movies Airplane! (1980) and Airplane II: The Sequel (1982). Her other movie roles include A Midsummer Night's Sex Comedy (1982), Lost in America (1985), What About Bob? (1991), Freddy Got Fingered (2001), A Master Builder (2014), and Marriage Story (2019). ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American stage actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Cincinnati
